## RACI Matrisi
```
R - Responsible: Gorevi yapan agent
A - Accountable: Sonuctan sorumlu (PM veya kullanici)
C - Consulted: Gorusu alinan
I - Informed: Haberdar edilecek

| Aktivite        | BA | Architect | Backend | Frontend | QA | Security | PM | User |
|-----------------|----|-----------|---------|---------|----|----------|----|------|
| US yazimi       | R  | C         | I       | I       | I  | C        | A  | A    |
| ADR/Kontrat     | C  | R         | C       | I       | I  | C        | A  | I    |
| DB Schema       | I  | C         | C       | I       | I  | I        | A  | I    |
| Backend kod     | I  | C         | R       | I       | I  | C        | A  | I    |
| Frontend UI     | I  | I         | C       | R       | I  | I        | A  | I    |
| Test            | I  | I         | C       | C       | R  | C        | A  | I    |
| Security review | I  | C         | I       | I       | C  | R        | A  | I    |
```

